Crotale staggered out.  The rifle at his chest.  "Names Crotale,  
where is Pacifix, somethings wrong."

--- In nbwrpg@y..., Yanshosh@a... wrote:
> ::Dion::
> 
> The shaking of the ship causes Dion to grab on to a wall for 
support, his systems reporting an energy drain long before he felt 
it. He frowns, walking off to the storage rooms (or wherever he was 
supposed to go) as instructed. They were barely off Cybertron and the 
mission was already going to the pit.
> 
> He reaches the storage rooms, entering and hearing a banging noise, 
turning to see dents forming in one of the doors. He frowns, walking 
to the door. Dion puts his hand on the door and concentrates, the 
hand beginning to heat up at an increadible rate untill his fingers 
melt through the door and he rips his hand back, taking the door with 
it and instantly aiming a large rifle at the bot beyond it.
> 
> "Who in the pit are you?" he asks, a bit drained as he looks at 
Crotale.
> 
> 
> 
>
